OL,3,CCricket match abandoned after runaway
OL,4,Cbull storms playing field
OL,6,FA cricket match in County Durham had
OL,7,Fto be abandoned after a runaway bull
OL,8,Fstormed the playing field and charged
OL,9,Fat players.
OL,11,FThe North East Premier League fixture
OL,12,Fat Burnopfield Cricket Club was called
OL,13,Foff on Saturday evening (4 July)
OL,14,Fdespite efforts to remove the animal
OL,15,Ffrom the ground.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
