PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1783714848
OL,3,CCricket match abandoned after runaway
OL,4,Cbull storms playing field
OL,6,FMartin Oswell, director of the
OL,7,FTyneside club, said the young bull,
OL,8,Fprobably weighing around 800kg, had
OL,9,Fescaped from a farm and travelled
OL,10,Fabout a mile to the playing field
OL,11,Fwhere it arrived at around 3pm.
OL,13,F"We couldn't get rid of it," Mr Oswell
OL,14,Ftold the Press Association.
OL,16,F"There was no chance that the game was
OL,17,Fgoing to restart before the cut-off
OL,18,Ftime.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@\O]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1783714848
OL,3,CCricket match abandoned after runaway
OL,4,Cbull storms playing field
OL,6,F"At first it was quite novel, it was
OL,7,Fquite funny ` but we never thought it
OL,8,Fwas going to impact on our game being
OL,9,Fabandoned."
OL,11,FThe bull's owner drove a cow to the
OL,12,Fcricket club in an effort to entice
OL,13,Fthe animal off the field but to no
OL,14,Favail, Mr Oswell added.
OL,16,F"The farmer who owns the bull arrived
OL,17,Fat the ground and tried at first to
OL,18,Fsort of cajole it and get it into a
OL,19,Fpen, but it failed," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@KO]xD@AOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1783714848
OL,3,CCricket match abandoned after runaway
OL,4,Cbull storms playing field
OL,6,F"The bull was very frightened ` it was
OL,7,Fspooked."
OL,9,FSafety concerns quickly arose as the
OL,10,Fbull could be seen charging at
OL,11,Fplayers, and farmers who attempted to
OL,12,Frecapture it.
OL,14,F"Two of the farmers tried to stop the
OL,15,Fbull and it actually hit one of them,"
OL,16,FMr Oswell said.
OL,18,F"He was OK but I mean the beast
OL,19,Fprobably weighed about 800kg.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@IO]vD@AOUwD@fO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1783714848
OL,3,CCricket match abandoned after runaway
OL,4,Cbull storms playing field
OL,6,F"It was a juvenile bull, incredibly
OL,7,Ffit, athletic ` quite frankly, it was
OL,8,Fquite dangerous."
OL,10,FPolice were eventually called to the
OL,11,Fscene before the bull left "of its own
OL,12,Faccord", Mr Oswell said.
OL,14,FBurnopfield CC had scored 226 runs
OL,15,Fagainst opponents Hetton Lyons when
OL,16,Fthe match was interrupted.
OL,18,F"We're second top of the North East
OL,19,FPremier League, so it was an important
OL,20,Fgame for us," Mr Oswell said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@QO]sD@\OUtD@GO]zD@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
