PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1783714848
OL,3,CCricket match abandoned after runaway
OL,4,Cbull storms playing field
OL,6,F"And it was a game that I think we had
OL,7,Fa really good chance of winning.
OL,9,F"It would have been a really, really
OL,10,Fgood game of cricket."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUrD@VO]
